{"tid":2022351,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣同意將參與世衛大會議題押後 讓大會先聚焦疫情","createTime":"2020-05-18T09:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T09:45:26.000Z","uid":70063,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c60d7e90241ac18f4537f3ccb2684201041fb0ef","tid":2022351,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T09:21:53.000Z","msg":"世衛大會視像會議本港時間傍晚六時召開，國家主席習近平將在會議開幕儀式上致辭。台灣不滿至今未獲邀參加會議，向世衛秘書處遞交抗議信。<br />\n<br />\n在台北，外長吳釗燮說，台灣已經付出一切努力，並獲空前的國際支持，不過，仍然未收到邀請函，對世衛秘書處屈服於大陸的壓力，並繼續無視台灣2300萬名民眾的健康權利，表示深切遺憾與強烈不滿。<br />\n<br />\n吳釗燮又說，明白今次會議的開會時間，受疫情影響而縮短，亦理解各國希望聚焦討論疫情，因此台灣支持友邦及理念相近國家的建議，將「台灣參與」的提議，等到世衛大會今年較後時間舉行實體會議時，再作討論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1526832-20200518.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1526832-20200518.htm&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCltn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=127e6a28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1526832-20200518.htm&h=6986ae8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1526832-20200518.htm</a>"},{"pid":"0bdad1050020940d0589cf4f6974f14e8a2b8de9","tid":2022351,"uid":2772,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T09:23:23.000Z","msg":"一個國家應有既器量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n賤種國永遠都唔會有"},{"pid":"9d38a4e3c82a6914b5f37fa7f54bfe7404e7eb56","tid":2022351,"uid":244332,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T09:23:39.000Z","msg":"風度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4500a83389ce265c890387484db12cdff090925","tid":2022351,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T09:24:50.000Z","msg":"而家比支那圍爐算啦<br />\n<br />\n小英兩日後再登基<br />\n到時萬國祝賀"},{"pid":"f5dbb31853a15a9ddb78ca37ef5aafd137cfdb39","tid":2022351,"uid":346806,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"re